<p>Looking for information on local laws on smoking? Try an organization called <a href="http://www.no-smoke.org" target="_blank">Americans for Nonsmokers Rights</a>.</p>
<p>Looking for more information on secondhand smoke? Check out these <a href="https://www.tobaccofreekids.org/what-we-do/us/smoke-free-laws" target="_blank">resources</a> from the Campaign for Tobacco-Free Kids or this <a href="https://www.cdc.gov/tobacco/data_statistics/by_topic/secondhand_smoke/index.htm " target="_blank">information</a> from the Centers for Disease Control and&nbsp;Prevention.</p>
